# Session log

Running log of Claude Code sessions on this repo. Append a new entry at the top each session — most recent first. Keep entries short: what changed, where we left off, what's queued next.

Format per entry:
```
## YYYY-MM-DD — short title
**By:** alireza | khashi  (who drove the session — tag so the other person's Claude knows who touched what)
**Did:** bullets of what was actually done (files touched, commands run, decisions made)
**State:** clean / dirty / blocked — current working state
**Next:** what to pick up on the next session
```

