## 2026-05-26 — Auth/profile/admin polish; mock-data audit
**By:** alireza
**Did:**
- **OTP signup flow** (backend + frontend). Backend: added `OtpPurpose.SIGNUP`, `PhoneSignupVerify` schema, `service.start_phone_signup` (silent-202 on taken phone — enumeration-safe), `service.complete_phone_signup` (verify OTP → create user → tokens), routes `POST /auth/signup/otp/{request,verify}`. Hot-patched into the running container (Docker Hub auth blocked from IR network so `--build` fails — used `docker cp`; rebuild properly once you have DH access). Frontend: 2-step `phone-signup` mode in `AuthView` with toggle buttons mirroring the `login`↔`phone-otp` pattern.
- **Email/phone login parity.** Backend `LoginRequest.email` → `identifier: str`; `service.authenticate` routes by `@` presence (email or `normalize_iranian_mobile`-ed phone). Frontend: input label "ایمیل یا شماره موبایل", `type=text`, sends `{identifier, password}`. **Breaking change for any other API consumer of `/auth/login`** — must send `identifier`, not `email`.
- **Profile page wired to real user.** `AccountDashboard` was rendering hardcoded "مهدی محمود" via stale localStorage seed. Fixed: derive `profileData` from `user` prop (with `useEffect([user])` re-sync), settings form converted from `defaultValue=...` to controlled inputs. Frontend `User` type/mapper gained `phone` (backend always returned it).
- **Per-user dashboard data.** `pets`/`wishlist`/`addresses` localStorage keys now namespaced as `petone_<thing>_<user.id>` so two accounts on same browser don't share data. Mock seed fallbacks removed — new users start empty. Old shared `*_v3` keys orphaned (harmless).
- **Orders wired to backend.** `auth.ts` got `listMyOrders()` (`authFetch('/orders')`). `AccountDashboard` fetches on `user?.id` change; the hardcoded `۱۲` count + 4 demo `<OrderCard>` JSX nodes replaced with real data / empty state. New `OrderCard` handles all 5 backend statuses (pending/paid/shipped/delivered/cancelled) with Persian labels.
- **Admin gate is now real auth.** Removed the passcode modal entirely (was bypassing the backend gate with hardcoded `1405`/`admin`/`1234`). `isAdmin` derives from `user.isAdmin` via `useEffect([user])`. URL `/admin` always sets view; the view renders dashboard or a clean "no access" page based on the flag. **Auto-redirect:** `onAuthSuccess` now routes admin users to `/admin` on login (no manual button). All 5 login/signup paths flow through this central decision.
- **Admin mock-data lies removed.** `orders` admin state: no more 5 fake "کامران امیری"-style seed entries. `stats.totalSales`: dropped fake `+7600000` base. `stats.customersCount`: dropped fake `145 + orders.length * 3` base. Metric sub-text: replaced "رشد ۲۳٪" / "۵۰ کاربر جدید آنلاین" with neutral descriptors. `categories`/`articles` were stripped briefly then reverted at user's request — these stay seeded (NAV_CATEGORIES + 3 sample articles) but their inits now treat empty cached arrays as "no cache" and reseed, to recover from any earlier strip-pass that left an empty in localStorage.
- **Avatar.** Replaced the hardcoded Unsplash CDN URL with an inline gray-silhouette SVG. No external CDN, neutral for every account.
- **Frontend 409 messaging fix.** `apiErrorToFa` used to render *every* 409 default as "این ایمیل قبلاً ثبت‌نام شده است". Now detects backend detail prefix (`Phone…` / `Email…`) and routes precisely. Default 409 fallback now neutral.
- **DB wipe + admin promotion.** Cleared 4 test users + their OTP/refresh rows. New user `keyvan.zalaghi@yahoo.com` (id=9, phone `9126547663`) marked `is_admin=true`.
- **SMS.ir.** Smoke-tested end-to-end via Iran network; sms.ir returns `status:1` (موفق) with valid messageIds but actual delivery never reached any of 3 test phones — alireza will resolve via sms.ir panel (template approval / blacklist / sender-line binding). App layer is correct, sms.py improvements still in place: param name `CODE` to match `#CODE#` template, richer error logging for HTTPStatusError + connect-timeout.

