**Admin panel TODO (in priority order):**
1. **Admin-scoped backend endpoints — none exist yet.** `GET /orders` returns only the current user's orders, so admin's orders tab and `stats.ordersCount` / `totalSales` show only the admin's own purchases. Need: `GET /admin/orders` (all orders, paginated), `GET /admin/customers` (so `customersCount` stops being 0), `GET /admin/sales/summary` (so totalSales is correctly aggregated). All gated by `Depends(get_current_admin)` (already exists in `app/dependencies.py`).
